Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.82,CN-op01-side,,0,0,0,,浮沉世界　如堕烟海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:45.28,CN-op01-side,,0,0,0,,一直寻觅　坚毅自强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.73,CN-op01-side,,0,0,0,,成为我想
