Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.27,0:04:47.56,jp,Mai,0,0,0,,お疲れ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.51,jp,Nozomi,0,0,0,,はい　チー
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.33,jp,Nozomi,0,0,0,,利奈も
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.05,jp,Rina,0,0,0,,なんで
